 ofParis's bid to host the Olympic Gameswas its simplicity: this great city already had the facilities required to host, and so many of the problems associated with building new venues - the spiralling costs, the environmental demands, the white elephants left scattered a decade later - would not be in play.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bookmarks\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"ofParis's bid\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Gameswas\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"its simplicity\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"this great city\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"the facilities\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the problems\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"new venues\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the spiralling costs\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"the environmental demands\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"the white elephants\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only one venue needed to be built from scratch: the Aquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only one venue\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The proposal written into the original bid was foran Olympic Aquatics Centreto seat 15,000 spectators, the minimum number required by swimming's governing body, Fina, for major international events.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The proposal\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the original bid\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Aquatics Centreto\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"15,000 spectators\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the minimum number\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming's governing body\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"Fina\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"major international events\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be based in the deprived northern suburb of Seine-Saint-Denis, the second poorest neighbourhood in France, an area of high crime and poverty, of low education and life expectancy, where only 50 per cent of children under 12 can swim.Long after the Games, the venue would leave a lasting legacy.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9801936446452019, \"rank\": 0.020198839154503077, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the deprived northern suburb\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the second poorest neighbourhood\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"an area\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"high crime\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"poverty\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"low education and life expectancy\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"only 50 per cent\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"a lasting legacy\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in 2020, the plan changed.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It became clear that the original budget of \\u20ac70m (\\u00a360m) was nowhere near what was required to build a small stadium fit for the Olympic Games and disassemble it afterwards.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the original budget\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"a small stadium fit\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So organisers took the decision to complete the project with only 5,000 seats, in order to cap their overspending at around \\u20ac175m (\\u00a3150m).\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"only 5,000 seats\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"their overspending\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant the Aquatics Centre no longer met Fina's 15,000-seat requirement for major events, or even came close.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"Fina's 15,000-seat requirement\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so Paris built a brand new Olympic venue, complete with a brand new Olympic pool, that will not host a single swimming race.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.519013719162491e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brand new Olympic venue\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand new Olympic pool\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"a single swimming race\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aquatics Centre will still host diving, synchronised swimming and some water polo qualifying rounds.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"synchronised swimming\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"some water polo qualifying rounds\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a striking piece of architecture, made of long timber frames which support a huge rooftop solar farm to power the venue, and inside it is full of recycled material to meet France's pitch for a green Games.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9801936446452019, \"rank\": 0.020198839154503077, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a striking piece\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"architecture\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"long timber frames\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge rooftop solar farm\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled material\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"a green Games\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the swimming itself has been relocated to the west of the city at La Defense Arena, a multi-purpose venue mainly used by rugby club Racing 92 and for staging concerts.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimming\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"the west\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"a multi-purpose venue\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby club\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"staging concerts\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taylor Swift performed her Eras Tour there in front of 180,000 people in May, before it was rapidly transformed into a swimming venue holding 15,000 fans for the Games.\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.659061723526278e-37, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Eras Tour\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"180,000 people\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimming venue\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"15,000 fans\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis will still get its legacy pools, facilities that are a welcome boost to the area.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", 