ng for four golds in Paris and carries a nation's expectations on broad shoulders.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3356, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.519013719162491e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four golds\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation's expectations\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"broad shoulders\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should he deliver, the pool will be a hallowed place, somewhere sporting history was made, which makes it all the more bizarre that his story will not unfold in Paris's impressive new Aquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3580, \"end\": 3585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.519013719162491e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"a hallowed place\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting history\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"his story\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is one symptom of an ailment that has troubled the Olympics for more than half a century, that of uncontrollable spending.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one symptom\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"an ailment\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3683}, {\"ngram\": \"more than half a century\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"uncontrollable spending\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3745}]}, {\"sentence\": 